I"<p>Cultura Viva Foundation and Alegre Global have started a new program to improve the morals standards and ethics of the public. The Way to Happiness is a 1980 booklet written by L. Ron Hubbard listing 21 moral precepts. Today it is the first moral code based on common sense, with the purpose to reverse the current moral decline in society and restore integrity and trust to humankind. This code of conduct can be followed by anyone, of any race, color, or creed and works to restore the bonds that unite humankind.</p>
